snippet.title: NOW is TIME TO LAUGH! - Super funny DOGS, CATS & BIRDS
snippet.description:
So super funny combination of cats, dogs and birds! These videos will make you laugh no matter what! Just look how all these dogs, cats and birds fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
